      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_155374458996889961.png",
                "id": "talent98480",
                "key": "Rapid Ritesword",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rapid Ritesword"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>. The first time this Skill is used this Round, heal the character for 2 HP if they have no more than 8 HP, but apply <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overawing Assault</span> to said character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Overawing Assault</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> If this character's HP is at least 6, then they will take 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/42bfd225eedc984bb1d4a4af99e3dcae_3020819802586908694.png",
                "id": "talent23108",
                "key": "Enigmatic Feint",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Enigmatic Feint"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Bogglecat Box</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/b718fd9ceee2d78fdf5d76f345458f71_5250004434211649394.png",
                "id": "talent31750",
                "key": "Magic Trick: Astonishing Shift",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Magic Trick: Astonishing Shift"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deals 1<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\"> Anemo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your active character takes DMG: </span>Decreases DMG taken by 1. (Once per Round)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your character(s) take </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>/<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">DMG: </span>Change the Elemental Type of this card to the element of the damage taken. (Once before leaving play)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6056697809650291234.png",
                "id": "talent46131",
                "key": "Bogglecat Box",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/bc84abe7e3d8d79c9b75a0de329313dc_5420012929478866802.png",
                "title": "Bogglecat Box"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Cryo DMG to all opposing chracters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl:</span> Deals 1 Hydro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Pyro DMG to all opposing characters except the target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Deals 1 Electro DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8818031795297604778.png",
                "id": "talent80205",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\"><br>Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.<br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\"><br>Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_417376777346822813.png",
                "id": "talent29869",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
